        "right_video_url": "",
        "Heading_size": "h2",
        "Heading_color": "#c0ccbe",
        "title": "HERITAGE",
        "video-sec-content-txt-1": "<p>In 1928, our family patriarch, Albertus Viljoen van der Merwe – “Alvi” to his friends – established a farm south of the town of Worcester, South Africa. Alvi’s son, Bertie, started wine production on the family farm and today the award-winning Alvi’s Drift wines are created by winemaker Alvi van der Merwe, Oupa Alvi’s grandson and namesake.</p><p>Our Albertus Viljoen Icon range showcases full-bodied, barrel-fermented wines of outstanding character and complexity.</p>",
        "button-txt": "ICON RANGE",
        "button_link": "shopify://collections/icon-range",
